videos.description: During the Pacers-76ers game Jordan Hill shakes off Nerlens Noel and finishes with a dunk.  A few plays later, Jahlil Okafor returns the favor and hits Hill with the "Dream Shake" and finishes with a floater.
videos.headline: Hill and Okafor channel their inner Olajuwon
